---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="404 - Page Not Found">
  <section class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 py-20 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-8xl font-bold text-accent">404</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-ink">페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다.</p>
    <p class="text-subtle">요청하신 페이지가 존재하지 않거나, 이동되었을 수 있습니다.</p>
    <a
      href="/"
      class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-line px-5 py-2.5 font-medium text-ink transition-colors hover:bg-surface"
    >
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="size-4" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M9.707 14.707a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414l4-4a1 1 0 011.414 1.414L7.414 9H15a1 1 0 110 2H7.414l2.293 2.293a1 1 0 010 1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
      </svg>
      홈으로 돌아가기
    </a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
